Knowledge Check 2.4
The Three Ways of DevOps are: the First Way - Accelerate Flow, the Second Way - Amplify Feedback, and the Third Way - Continuous Integration. Please select the correct answer.
a. True
*b. False correct 

NOTE: http://itrevolution.com/the-three-ways-principles-underpinning-devops/
The Third Way is about creating a culture that fosters two things: continual experimentation, taking risks and learning from failure; and understanding that repetition and practice is the prerequisite to mastery.


